entities.name: dobby
entities.description: Dobby is an elf who is known to be loyal and protective of Harry Potter. He is described as looking up at Harry with a slightly cross-eyed expression and trying to bang his head off Harry's knees.

entities.name: umbridge
entities.description: Umbridge is a character who induces fear in Dobby, suggesting she may be a powerful or intimidating figure. She has not yet discovered the secret about the D.A.

relationships.description: Dobby fears Umbridge, as evidenced by his reaction when Harry asks if she has found out about their secret. Dobby's behavior suggests that he is terrified of her.
